<br>
-Falcon <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#aaaaaa><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub25.ezboard.com/ujefm.showPublicProfile?language=EN>jefm</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Karbonite</span><br> <font color=#336699>(9/22/01 9:05:09 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub25.ezboard.com/fpolykarbonbbsfrm26.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=328.topic&index=3>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: A Poem on the Mind...intrigued???</span><hr size=1> I noticed that it felt like a song in some parts...hmm ten syllables per line <p>--
